Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.-01,0:00:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.49,0:00:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.43,0:00:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:01:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:39.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba" "Erumalu" "Nanohana" "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed since\Na single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people took up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:02:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The once-green city of\NErumalu now lies in ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To stop the rebel army, Luffy and\Ncompany now head into the desert
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for Yuba, the oasis town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Adventure in the Country of Sand! The\NMonsters that Live in the Scorching Land"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning up...\NSweat won't even come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit moaning so much, Luffy.\NYou'll only tire yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess he's not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on...\NI can't take hot weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine in cold weather, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 'cause of all that fur...\NYou should take off that animal suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Don't turn big!\NOr else I won't pull ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling a monster,\NHumongo-Nose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be stupid!\NI-I'll have you know this nose--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just turn back already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to be having\Na hard time, Vivi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born and raised here,\Nso it doesn't bother me much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's with all these hills?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured a desert would be more flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very old desert,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so some sand dunes here\Nare over 300 meters high.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Three hundred meters?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder this is like\Nclimbing mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much... It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one drink, Luffy.\NJust one mouthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have some, too!\NThat was 13 mouthfuls just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! You just had some! I'm next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting!\NYou'll only waste strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But she started it!\N--It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! This is because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so greedy!\NIt's still raw! Don't eat that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Just a minute,\Nit'll be ready soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, looks pretty good!\N--Get away, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!\NCheapskate! Let us eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so hot during the day!\NWhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With nothing to block\Nout the temperature,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the desert scorches during the day\Nbut falls below freezing at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The desert is fraught\Nwith unpredictable dangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Look at all those stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see stars\Non your winter island?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter island skies are always\Ncovered with thick snow clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I've never seen\Nso many stars before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the luxury of\Nlooking at stars right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold weather doesn't bother me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you wear\Nsuch a warm suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help that you're so fluffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit making fun of reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper. Don't turn big.\NWe need your warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Warm, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a real surprise for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Luffy-san.\NI was surprised too, at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's that he isn't captain-like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or that normal pirate captains are\Nrespected by their crewmates...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just this afternoon, a simple\Ndrink of water caused that big fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The longer I've been with them,\Nthe more I've come to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Luffy does things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't changed a bit\Nsince he was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how he seems,\Npeople always gather around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he's my little brother,\Nhe has a mysterious charm to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. You already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He and I do go way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were worried that\NI was concerned, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But it looks like I didn't\Nneed to worry after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I found a shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a shrimp?! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shrimp don't live in the desert!\N--See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right!\NIs it a "desert shrimp"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It looks yummy!\N--Hey, now! Are they edible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably! Crawfish are edible, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a real shrimp before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Luffy-san! Throw that away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That'd be a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a scorpion! It's small\Nbut it's very poisonous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if it stings you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. It's not edible? How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You can have it.\N--Don't give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\NI should've mentioned it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's... coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is the wind picking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide behind the rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:07:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm! A sandstorm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?! Deserts are nothing but storms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to mention it, but sandstorms\Nare one of the desert's dangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mention these things sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't people get some rest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sanji! Let's have a lunch!\NA Pirate Boxed Lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:09:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. Not until Vivi-chan says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Vivi! Let's eat!\NI'm out of strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're only one-tenth of\Nthe way to Yuba, Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dumb! Haven't\Nyou heard of this proverb?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you're hungry, eat!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar! Quit making stuff up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you say we take a\Nbreak at the next rocks we find?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Let's hurry to the next rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever wins rock-paper-scissors\Nhas to carry everyone's stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit deciding things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't the loser carry the stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! You went after!\N--Woohoo! I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Heavy... So heavy... And hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won rock-paper-scissors,\Nso why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you won.\NNow shut up and haul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:10:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drop it, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocks spotted a small ways ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For reals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break time! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shade! Feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get you a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's lots of hurt birds\Nthat can't move! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright! Let's go, Chopper!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta help the birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Birds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy-san! Don't tell\Nme these birds are--!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All our stuff is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been had...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth! There really\Nwere dying birds here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I should've\Nmentioned it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warusagi birds are\N"desert bandits" that trick travelers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and steal their belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:12:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Birds playing dead?!\NThat's dishonest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's how they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They tricked me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Is that all you can\Nsay for yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were three days\Nof provisions in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you just had to let some\Ndamn birds steal everyone's stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,smack in the middle of this desert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How're we supposed to cross the\Ndesert without food or water now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault. They tricked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your brain less than a bird's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this,\Nit's best to let them have it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a short break.\NThis heat is what has them fuming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll manage food-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing that'll kill us.\NLet's just put it out of our minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Just thinking makes me thirstier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us our stuff back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Don't chase them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Will you be\Nable to come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You can't get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:14:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mystery desert plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You want me to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing you didn't get eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:15:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The birds got away while\NI was beating these guys up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The desert sure is full\Nof strange creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, camel. What're you doing\Nout here all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking Luffy so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Do you think he got lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:16:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a horrible sense of\Ndirection but always has to run off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are so many desert\Ndangers he doesn't know about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, isn't he hungry\Nfrom not eating anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a lost cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my little brother's ineptness.\NI apologize for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck finding him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this rumbling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another sandstorm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! That's--!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he on a camel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?! What's that chasing him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems more like\Nsomething's in the sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sandora Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A what now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the largest of the\Nreptiles living in the desert
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they wait under the\Nsand for their prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have sharp claws and fangs,\Nbut they hardly ever use them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason being that they tend\Nto swallow their prey whole
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because they're so large!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really does have a gift\Nfor attracting trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Setting aside the camel for the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what star was he born under to be\Nable to attract trouble like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Camel! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy! Is it too much for you?!\N--We'll lend a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I brought some meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes, lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tatsu...\N--êpaule...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...Maki!\N--...Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You didn't have to go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they're fighting,\Nyou almost pity the monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to mention it,\Nbut Sandora Dragons hunt in pairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mention these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ace!\N--Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:19:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. If that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out! These rocks\Nare natural frying pans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's with the camel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was getting eaten by a mystery\Nplant when I was chasing the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem to be a wild camel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It even has a saddle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.28,0:19:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He gave me a ride\Nwhen I escaped from Katorea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! We can ride it?!\NThat'll make things easier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that'll be a real help!\NLooks like it could carry two people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camels do go hand-in-hand with deserts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be the first one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I am a freedom-loving,\Nhard-boiled, compassionate camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping me out of that pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can give you a lift,\Nbut no men allowed!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's a punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You let Chopper ride you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm manly!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Quit being stupid!\N--Why, you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!\NMy crewmates are so ill-bred!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good boy!\NWhat should we call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Idiot!\N--Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doofus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lashes" it is, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, that's the weirdest one of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Get on, Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can still walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervy camel! Pervy camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervy camel! Pervy camel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we should make a little better time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get to Yuba as fast as\Nwe can to talk to the rebel army!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giddyup, Lashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, guys! If you get separated,\Nyou'll never leave the desert alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit being stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this side of Nami-san, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After them! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get on, Chopper!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the adventurers\NI dreamed of when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue on to the ends of emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:22:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scoop up my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sand and time\Nthat spills from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me that this is\Nwhat I was born to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue swimming\Nat a near-tumbling speed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we wash up someday\Non a white sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:23:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So hot...\N--Nami-san! How far did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.14,0:23:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're completely separated now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\NI don't see Ace, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do you think he got separated?\N--What a troublesome big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?! What's that?!\N--Do you see Nami's group?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship! A pirate ship in the sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enter the Desert Pirates!\NThe Men Who Live Freely"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
